{"tid":1368363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727元朗 我覺得係最有可能中共嫁禍我地既好日","createTime":"2019-07-26T12:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T14:11:13.000Z","uid":64810,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"92e1da5632cef7a9820492f23b8729fa7674c482","tid":1368363,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:59:15.000Z","msg":"大家都Feel到聽日可以好鬼 , 班白衫依家又係圍頭到開緊會..<br />\n<br />\n所以聽日大家<br />\n1.一定要盡力拍低有可疑既事,留意可疑既人(由其係北佬樣個D),甚至留意貨車<br />\n2.有良好既通訊 有冇巴打開元朗tg?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.唔好做犯法行為,做個和理膠, 唔可以學白衫咁無差別打人<br />\n4.輕裝上陣, 帶遮, 哨子/神器, 電筒, 水<br />\n5.一定要記得 唔入村,唔遊行,唔挑釁<br />\n6.記住元朗消防既電話,btw消防局個邊有狗車(<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1367613/page/24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1367613/page/24</a>)<br />\n7.最好唔好單獨行 小心為上 唔好落單<br />\n<br />\n等其實巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"67fe823a996bd2832102ede360720ba669a7559f","tid":1368363,"uid":262125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:59:48.000Z","msg":"我估我今晚都會瞓唔着"},{"pid":"d46769cb68bac070cdbeb750802d580894e4586a","tid":1368363,"uid":34519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:59:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"550cc1d5d2f4228f97b2d6fe8f42c0d46431e51d","tid":1368363,"uid":212182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:59:57.000Z","msg":"push，如果白衫故意挑釁，我地要冷靜理性對應"},{"pid":"5c3aa9b26c3a9b4790601b385656a444e8a1b7d6","tid":1368363,"uid":36158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"我唔撚理<br />\n我聽日直入元朗"},{"pid":"2881146a7d233b9b6ebbfac1a8bdb549ae6face9","tid":1368363,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face